--[ERIKA] Okay!

00:00:56.014 --> 00:00:57.474 position:50% align:center
[TOUKO]
Ooh, yeah, love that!

00:00:57.557 --> 00:00:59.392 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Riri! Morning!

00:00:59.476 --> 00:01:00.935 position:50% align:center
