who'll even get to see it.

00:01:17.535 --> 00:01:20.163 position:50% align:center
Yeah, not much class
time till the festival!

00:01:20.246 --> 00:01:22.040 position:50% align:center
I'm totally lovin' that, though!

00:01:22.123 --> 00:01:23.500 position:50% align:center
Yeah, ditto!

00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:25.251 position:50% align:center
Right?

00:01:27.754 --> 00:01:29.923 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] Let's all go out
there and practice hard!

00:03:03.058 --> 00:03:07.020 position:50% align:center
