00:03:16.946 --> 00:03:19.282 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
You mean, like this?

00:03:20.283 --> 00:03:23.370 position:50% align:center
[YASUKO]
Mm-hm. Yeah, that's it.

00:03:23.453 --> 00:03:24.788 position:50% align:center
