00:03:39.177 --> 00:03:41.513 position:50% align:center
I did it!

00:03:41.596 --> 00:03:43.932 position:50% align:center
They're so cute!

00:03:44.015 --> 00:03:46.434 position:50% align:center
That was easier than
I thought it would be.

00:03:46.518 --> 00:03:48.520 position:50% align:center
[NEKO]
So soft and fluffy.

00:03:48.603 --> 00:03:49.437 position:50% align:center
[KEI giggles]

00:03:49.521 --> 00:03:51.564 position:50% align:center
So cool, Nawashiro!

00:03:51.648 --> 00:03:54.067 position:50% align:center
I mean, for the life of me,
I couldn't understand

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:57.654 position:50% align:center
what we were using
this vinyl tape for!

00:03:57.737 --> 00:04:00.824 position:50% align:center
