00:04:02.909 --> 00:04:05.495 position:50% align:center
I'm so glad! Okay!

00:04:05.578 --> 00:04:08.832 position:50% align:center
Now, let's get out there
and cheer everybody on!

00:04:08.915 --> 00:04:09.749 position:50% align:center
[YASUKO, KEI]
Yeah!

00:04:09.833 --> 00:04:13.461 position:50% align:center
[NEKO breathing deeply]

00:04:17.298 --> 00:04:19.592 position:50% align:center
You're in the tennis club,
right, Shijou?

00:04:19.676 --> 00:04:22.595 position:50% align:center
Yeah. What about you?
Have you ever played?

00:04:22.679 --> 00:04:25.098 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] Our summer house
has a court, so, a little.

00:04:25.181 --> 00:04:26.516 position:50% align:center
Summer house?

00:04:26.599 --> 00:04:29.310 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] Yeah. I was only
playing around for fun, though.

00:04:29.394 --> 00:04:34.649 position:50% align:center
Listen, don't worry, I'll do
my very best not to trip you up.

00:04:34.733 --> 00:04:36.109 position:50% align:center
[RIONA]
Oh, you won't.

00:04:36.192 --> 00:04:38.611 position:50% align:center
It's not like I'm
that good at it, either.

00:04:40.488 --> 00:04:43.408 position:50% align:center
Well, your tennis outfit
looks super cute.

00:04:45.952 --> 00:04:48.371 position:50% align:center
Oh. Well, thank you.

00:04:52.667 --> 00:04:54.002 position:50% align:center
