if you open with that stuff.

00:07:26.029 --> 00:07:29.699 position:50% align:center
You need to start with
some simple choreography!

00:07:29.783 --> 00:07:31.826 position:50% align:center
What kind of choreography?

00:07:31.910 --> 00:07:33.912 position:50% align:center
Hold on, you ain't never
seen the stand dances

00:07:33.995 --> 00:07:35.997 position:50% align:center
they do over at Koshien?

00:07:36.081 --> 00:07:38.249 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Mm...

00:07:38.333 --> 00:07:40.502 position:50% align:center
[AYUMI sighs]
For example--

00:07:43.755 --> 00:07:49.219 position:50% align:center
Stuff like this, and like
this, and these moves!

00:07:49.302 --> 00:07:51.262 position:50% align:center
[ALL gasp]

00:07:51.346 --> 00:07:52.972 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Wow! That was so cool!

00:07:53.056 --> 00:07:55.058 position:50% align:center
You're easily impressed, huh?

00:07:55.141 --> 00:07:57.602 position:50% align:center
