most basic of the basics?

00:08:00.689 --> 00:08:03.733 position:50% align:center
'Cause it gives me a chance
to watch everyone practice.

00:08:03.817 --> 00:08:05.360 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:08:05.443 --> 00:08:08.822 position:50% align:center
Well, why don't we all try that?

00:08:08.905 --> 00:08:12.492 position:50% align:center
Here we go! Ready, okay!

00:08:12.575 --> 00:08:17.247 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI, NEKO, YASUKO, KEI]
Fight on! Fight on! Ayumi!

00:08:17.330 --> 00:08:22.002 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI, NEKO, YASUKO, KEI]
Fight on! Fight on! Minoru!

00:08:22.085 --> 00:08:23.378 position:50% align:center
Wow!

00:08:23.461 --> 00:08:26.589 position:50% align:center
I think I can actually
feel a surge of power!

00:08:26.673 --> 00:08:29.467 position:50% align:center
Well, it's better
than it was before.

00:08:29.551 --> 00:08:31.886 position:50% align:center
Oh, thanks, Tougeguchi!

00:08:31.970 --> 00:08:35.056 position:50% align:center
Want me to help with your table
tennis practice in return?

00:08:35.140 --> 00:08:36.224 position:50% align:center
[AYUMI]
N-No, thank you!

00:08:36.307 --> 00:08:38.309 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
C'mon, no need to be modest!

00:08:38.393 --> 00:08:41.271 position:50% align:center
It seems awfully
lively over there.

00:08:44.065 --> 00:08:47.610 position:50% align:center
Hebimori! Hotaru!

00:08:47.694 --> 00:08:49.029 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:08:49.112 --> 00:08:50.363 position:50% align:center
Hi there.

00:08:52.657 --> 00:08:55.326 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI panting]

00:09:00.373 --> 00:09:01.416 position:50% align:center
[OSHIZU]
Hm?

00:09:01.499 --> 00:09:05.295 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Fight on! Fight on! Oshizu!

00:09:05.378 --> 00:09:09.132 position:50% align:center
Fight on! Fight on! Hotaru!

00:09:09.215 --> 00:09:12.677 position:50% align:center
--Fight on! Fight on! Oshizu!
--[OSHIZU] Whoa, hang on.

00:09:12.761 --> 00:09:16.389 position:50% align:center
Fight on! Fight on! Hotaru!

00:09:16.473 --> 00:09:21.227 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Fight on! Fight on! Oshizu.

00:09:21.311 --> 00:09:28.026 position:50% align:center
Fight on! Fight on! Hotaru!

00:09:31.363 --> 00:09:33.406 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:09:36.868 --> 00:09:41.373 position:50% align:center
You're awesome! Thanks, Hotaru!

00:09:41.456 --> 00:09:43.375 position:50% align:center
Guess they made a connection.

00:09:44.918 --> 00:09:46.670 position:50% align:center
[YASUKO]
We sure got some great advice.

00:09:46.753 --> 00:09:47.837 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Yeah!

00:09:47.921 --> 00:09:49.506 position:50% align:center
Cheering can't just
be about the calls.

00:09:49.589 --> 00:09:52.384 position:50% align:center
There's gotta be a dancing
element to it, too!

00:09:52.467 --> 00:09:55.261 position:50% align:center
So, maybe we'll be able
to do a few different things!

00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:57.347 position:50% align:center
--[YASUKO] Like what?
--[school bell rings]

00:09:57.430 --> 00:10:00.266 position:50% align:center
--I dunno. Maybe, like...
--[school bell rings]

00:10:00.350 --> 00:10:02.477 position:50% align:center
Sorry, everyone,
but I need to go practice

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:04.145 position:50% align:center
with the basketball team now.

00:10:04.229 --> 00:10:05.647 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah.

00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:08.149 position:50% align:center
And I need to head
to the dojo later.

00:10:08.233 --> 00:10:09.192 position:50% align:center
To the dojo?

00:10:09.275 --> 00:10:10.694 position:50% align:center
All right, then!

00:11:20.347 --> 00:11:26.895 position:50% align:center
[NEKO panting]

00:11:26.978 --> 00:11:29.856 position:50% align:center
So nice and cool.

00:11:29.939 --> 00:11:32.108 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:11:32.192 --> 00:11:33.610 position:50% align:center
Good cheering, everyone,

00:11:33.693 --> 00:11:36.363 position:50% align:center
but I think I'm gonna go
watch Hitomi's practice now.

00:11:36.446 --> 00:11:38.782 position:50% align:center
See you later.

00:11:38.865 --> 00:11:39.866 position:50% align:center
See ya.

00:11:43.828 --> 00:11:45.914 position:50% align:center
She's so hyped.

00:11:46.956 --> 00:11:48.083 position:50% align:center
[KEI]
Definitely.

00:11:48.166 --> 00:11:52.337 position:50% align:center
That was a pretty
tough practice, huh?

00:11:52.420 --> 00:11:55.882 position:50% align:center
[NEKO] I can't move.
I just want a bath.

00:11:55.965 --> 00:11:57.425 position:50% align:center
[KEI giggles]

00:11:57.509 --> 00:11:58.760 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Okay!

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.935 position:50% align:center
Akebi?

00:12:38.508 --> 00:12:42.429 position:50% align:center
Hey, Shijou, looks like
a court just opened up.

00:12:42.512 --> 00:12:44.514 position:50% align:center
You ready to get started?

00:12:44.597 --> 00:12:46.516 position:50% align:center
[RIONA]
Um. Sure!

00:12:57.819 --> 00:13:00.155 position:50% align:center
[RIONA] Until I started
studying for entrance exams

00:13:00.238 --> 00:13:02.532 position:50% align:center
two years ago, I had
played hardball tennis

00:13:02.615 --> 00:13:03.908 position:50% align:center
all through school.

00:13:03.992 --> 00:13:06.453 position:50% align:center
Of course, I'm sure
everyone expects me

00:13:06.536 --> 00:13:08.663 position:50% align:center
to do great in the
athletic festival.

00:13:17.797 --> 00:13:19.591 position:50% align:center
[RIONA] Can skills really
degrade this much

00:13:19.674 --> 00:13:22.135 position:50% align:center
in just two years?

00:13:22.218 --> 00:13:24.220 position:50% align:center
I spend my club time
picking up balls

00:13:24.304 --> 00:13:27.015 position:50% align:center
and doing practice swings,
so I didn't notice.

00:13:27.098 --> 00:13:28.558 position:50% align:center
[RIONA sighs]

00:13:33.021 --> 00:13:35.440 position:50% align:center
I'm really sorry I keep missing.

00:13:35.523 --> 00:13:38.068 position:50% align:center
Nah, don't worry about it.

00:13:49.162 --> 00:13:50.872 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Here, have some.

00:13:52.916 --> 00:13:55.251 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
It's my very favorite black tea.

00:13:55.335 --> 00:13:57.545 position:50% align:center
I think it should
help you calm down.

00:13:57.629 --> 00:13:59.964 position:50% align:center
Oh, that's so nice.

00:14:08.014 --> 00:14:09.599 position:50% align:center
It's good.

00:14:12.143 --> 00:14:14.104 position:50% align:center
[BOTH giggle]

00:14:14.187 --> 00:14:15.271 position:50% align:center
