Here it comes!

00:14:15.355 --> 00:14:19.359 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Oh. You took a two-year break?

00:14:19.442 --> 00:14:21.403 position:50% align:center
I don't think
you lost your skills.

00:14:21.486 --> 00:14:25.532 position:50% align:center
