I got a lot taller!

00:14:29.411 --> 00:14:34.207 position:50% align:center
And it wasn't just my height!
Other things, too!

00:14:37.168 --> 00:14:40.338 position:50% align:center
My mom said that
I'm developing well,

00:14:40.422 --> 00:14:41.965 position:50% align:center
better than most.

00:14:42.048 --> 00:14:45.176 position:50% align:center
That's not something
to feel bad about, though.

00:14:45.260 --> 00:14:47.887 position:50% align:center
[RIONA]
She also said that, but...

00:14:51.349 --> 00:14:53.351 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Fight on!

00:14:56.229 --> 00:14:58.023 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
How was that?

00:14:58.106 --> 00:15:00.400 position:50% align:center
[KEI]
Sounded good.

00:15:00.483 --> 00:15:01.860 position:50% align:center
[RIONA]
Look at her.

00:15:01.943 --> 00:15:03.820 position:50% align:center
Akebi is so slender.

00:15:03.903 --> 00:15:07.198 position:50% align:center
Ah! Hey, Shijou! Looking good!

00:15:07.282 --> 00:15:10.410 position:50% align:center
It's amazing that you can
serve from that high up!

00:15:10.493 --> 00:15:14.080 position:50% align:center
